<ol>
<li>Start <strong>Outlook</strong>.</li>
<li>On the Tools menu, click <strong>E-mail Accounts</strong>.</li>
<li>Click View or change existing e-mail accounts, and then click <strong>Next</strong>.</li>
<li>Click your account, and then click <strong>Change</strong>.</li>
<li>Click <strong>More Settings</strong>.</li>
<li>Click the <strong>Advanced tab</strong>.</li>
</ol>
<br style="clear: both;" />
</div>



